---
title: Double Seared Salmon & Golden Curry Yoghurt with Spring Onion Salad & Lime
description: This vibrant meal is a celebration of fresh, flaky salmon. It doesn’t take much for it to really shine - we’ve paired it with a fresh and crunchy spring onion-speckled salad. Don’t forget the golden yoghurt though - a dusting of curry powder and a drizzle of honey really boost the flavour of this creamy accompaniment.

*This recipe is under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
